{\pard\plain\s17\ql\sb120\sa120\keep\widctlpar\f0\fs24\sl240\slmult1 \sb60 \fi0 {\b Definition 3.2} {\i {\b Strong connectedness}: Given <<:$G$:>>, a state <<:$\\theta$:>> has strong connectedness if and only if for every pair of Rebels, there is a path consisting of Rebels to connect them. }\par
