}\pard\plain\s0\qj\widctlpar\f0\fs24\sl240\slmult1 \sb60 \fi0 The equilibrium in Theorem \~{\field{\*\fldinst{\lang1024 REF BMthm_main_result \\* MERGEFORMAT }}{\fldrslt{2}}} is constructive. According to definition \~{\field{\*\fldinst{\lang1024 REF BMDef_expost_efficient \\* MERGEFORMAT }}{\fldrslt{2.3}}}, I will construct the equilibrium path first, then construct the in-path and off-path beliefs, and then checking if the strategies and belief system indeed constitute an equilibrium. I begin with an overview of equilibrium construction, and then illustrate such construction. The whole equilibrium strategies and the omitted proofs are all in Appendix. \par
